metadata.name: BoneStak #1
metadata.description:
BoneStak is a collection of 1000 unique NFTs created by the Stakita Core Team. These skeletal K-9s are composed of unique trait categories consisting of items that range from sweatshirts, accessories and hats, to more rarer items like armour and iconic retro fits!

BoneStak NFT holders will receive various perks and privelidges within its developments, along with an array of giveaways and raffles within the community!

For more information about our NFT and token, visit Stakita.net!
